  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca \u0d86\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An increase in covid infected people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Health departments say that there is an increase in the number of Covid patients reported from the country.",
        "It is also clear from the statistics published by the Epidemiology Department that there has been some increase in the number of Covid-infected people reported in the past two weeks.",
        "After the control of the covid epidemic situation in Sri Lanka, the number of infected people reported daily decreased to less than 10 until last month, but now the number of infected people has increased to between 15-25 daily.",
        "19 people infected with Covid were reported yesterday (14) and on the 13th there were 23 people infected, on the 11th there were 19 people and 1 death infected with Covid, on the 10th there were 17 people infected, on the 9th there were 21 people, on the 8th there were 18 people, and on the 7th there were 20 people infected and one death. It is shown in the reports issued by the Epidemiology Department.",
        "The reports also state that 393 people infected with Covid are receiving treatment in hospitals and at home as of yesterday (14).",
        "When we made an inquiry in this regard, a spokesperson of Mulleriya IDH Hospital said that currently 24 people infected with Covid are being treated there.",
        "The spokesman also mentioned that the number of infected people treated at the hospital had dropped to between 1 and 4.",
        "About 6 cricketers, including the former captain of the Sri Lankan cricket team, Angelo Mathews, were also infected with Covid in the past few days."
      ],
